<item>
            <title>[LU-1200] 2.2.50 client doesn&apos;t build for SLES11 SP0 (2.6.27.19-5.1)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1200</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In SLES11 SP0 (2.6.27.19-5.1), .page_mkwrite uses struct page * instead of struct vm_fault * as its second parameter. Lustre need to detect it so that it can build patchless client for SLES11 SP0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>SLES11 SP0 (2.6.27.19-5.1)</environment>
        <key id="13506">LU-1200</key>
